Class RobotSensorsData

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.RobotSensorsData

  • public class RobotSensorsData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to store and update the data sent by the robot everytime new ones are received from the RP6 robot
    Author:
    Valentin
